Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:36.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}澄んだ空を　呼んでくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:43.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}行き先なら　もう決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:49.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}握るたづな　熱くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:54.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}迷いを打ち消して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:57.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}心動かすのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:23:02.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}いつでも君なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:06.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}信じてみたくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:09.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}出会いがまたひとつ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.79,0:23:14.75,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}明日をかえてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:22.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}願い溢れる度に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:27.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}ふわり風が吹いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:33.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}新しいページ　めくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:40.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}誰も知らないのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:45.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}一緒に見つけたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.39,0:23:55.15,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}君が描く未来を
